  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This observational study includes questionnaires send to doctors in all units treating
      pediatric patients with mechanical ventilation in Finland. Additionally all units treating
      pediatric patients with mechanical ventilation are invited to perform a quality control-like
      follow up for 3 months. Patient identity data is not collected, and no interventions to
      treatment are made.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
